                    </div>

                    <div class="sec-title">DP State Definitions</div>
                    <div class="info-box">
                        <strong>Classic (LC 53):</strong> dp[i] = max subarray sum ending at i<br>
                        Recurrence: dp[i] = max(nums[i], dp[i−1] + nums[i]) &nbsp;·&nbsp; Preferred: bottom-up, O(1) space<br><br>
                        <strong>Deletion variant (LC 1186):</strong><br>
                        dp_noDelete[i] = max sum ending at i, no deletion used<br>
                        dp_oneDelete[i] = max sum ending at i, exactly one element deleted<br>
                        dp_noDelete[i] = max(nums[i], dp_noDelete[i−1] + nums[i])<br>
                        dp_oneDelete[i] = max(dp_noDelete[i−1], dp_oneDelete[i−1] + nums[i]) &nbsp;← delete nums[i] OR continue after a prior deletion<br>
                        Preferred: bottom-up, O(1) rolling variables
                    </div>

