                        <tr><td class="num-cell">25</td><td><span class="l5">⚠️Trap</span></td><td><a class="lc-link" href="https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-increasing-subsequence/" target="_blank">LC 300</a></td><td class="prob-name trap-name">⚠️ Longest Increasing Subsequence</td><td><span class="diff-m">Med</span></td><td></td><td class="variant-cell">⚠️ Non-contiguous — Kadane's is wrong</td><td class="insight">LIS skips elements; contiguous invariant violated; use patience sort / O(n log n) DP</td></tr>
