                        <tr><td class="num-cell">42</td><td><span class="l4">Hard</span></td><td>5</td><td>Custom</td><td class="prob-name trap-name">🔧 Minimum Cost Segment Cover (CHT)</td><td><span class="diff-h">Hard</span></td><td></td><td class="variant-cell">Convex Hull Trick (CHT)</td><td class="insight">Hard: dp[i] = min(dp[j] + (i-j)*a[i]) → expand to min(dp[j] − j*a[i]) + i*a[i]; CHT collapses inner loop. Lines y = −j·x + dp[j]; query at x = a[i]; O(1) amortised with monotone queries. See full statement below</td></tr>
