                        S.No 24 (1981 bitset) → S.No 26 (meet-in-the-middle) → S.No 29 (custom bitset). Implement bitset knapsack in both Python (int as bitset) and C++ (std::bitset&lt;N&gt;). Implement meet-in-the-middle from scratch.<br><br>
