                        &bull; Stage 3: AtCoder Educational DP Contest V "Subtree" &mdash; two-state tree DP with connectivity constraint<br>
                        &bull; Stage 4: Codeforces Edu Round 67 F "Hive" &mdash; implicit tree from interval structure; tree DP on containment tree<br>
